<para style="q1">

<verse number="30" style="v" />As for God: his way is perfect. The word of Yahweh is pure!</para>

<para style="q1">He is a shield to everyone who takes refuge in him.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="31" style="v" />For who is God except Yahweh? Who is a rock except our God?</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="32" style="v" />It is God who puts strength on me like a belt, who places the blameless person on his path.</para>
